{"title":"Implement fee sharing model","description":"Currently all rewards go to LPs, reducing utility value for token holders who are just getting diluted for nothing. 

Split token rewards and fees 50/50 between LPs and token holders as per Curve Finance token model - rewards can optionally be time weighted to create velocity sinks, and incentivise long term thinking.



"}

